OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FWords by Lucy L. Middleton
OL,9,FThe International Energy Agency has
OL,10,Fagreed to release a record 400 million
OL,11,Fbarrels of oil to combat a spike in
OL,12,Fprices as the war in Iran continued
OL,13,Finto its 13th day.
OL,15,FOil prices passed $100 per barrel on
OL,16,FMonday this week ` the highest since
OL,17,FJuly 2022 ` before dropping to around
OL,18,F$90 (#67.23) following the IEA's
OL,19,Fannouncement on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
