CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FThe Strait of Hormuz - which would
OL,8,Ftypically see 200 oil and gas tankers
OL,9,Fpass through it on a normal day - has
OL,10,Fbeen effectively closed by the
OL,11,Fconflict, with two fuel tankers struck
OL,12,Fnear the Iraqi port of Umm Qasr in the
OL,13,Fearly hours of Thursday.
OL,15,FMore than 2,000 people have died in
OL,16,Fthe war so far, including 1,300 people
OL,17,Fin Iran and 634 in Lebanon, 12 in
OL,18,FIsrael and seven from the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
