OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FWhat is the International Energy
OL,13,FAgency (IEA)?
OL,15,FThe IEA is a Paris-based
OL,16,Fintergovernmental organisation founded
OL,17,Fin 1974 to help co-ordinate a
OL,18,Fcollective response to major
OL,19,Fdisruptions in the supply of oil.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
