PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FIt does this by requiring countries to
OL,8,Fhave emergency oil stocks equivalent
OL,9,Fto at least 90 days of net imports.
OL,11,FCountries that want to be members also
OL,12,Fneed a demand restraint programme - a
OL,13,Fset of temporary measures to rapidly
OL,14,Freduce the energy usage - that will
OL,15,Fcut national oil consumption by up to
OL,16,F10%, among other terms.
OL,18,FEach nation must also be able to
OL,19,Fcontribute a proportional share -
OL,20,Fbased on its national consumption - of
OL,21,Foil to the global market if necessary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FThe IEA also has associated countries,
OL,8,Fwhich partner with the organisation
OL,9,Fbut are not bound by the same rules,
OL,10,Fand it produces analysis reports and
OL,11,Fdelivers policy advice.
OL,13,FWhich countries are members?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
