CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FThe IEA currently has 32 member
OL,8,Fcountries, the majority of which are
OL,9,FEuropean. These are: The UK, Austria,
OL,10,FBelgium, Czechia, Denmark, Estonia,
OL,11,FFinland, France, Germany, Greece,
OL,12,FHungary, Ireland, Italy, Latvia,
OL,13,FLithuania, Luxembourg, the
OL,14,FNetherlands, Norway, Poland, Portugal,
OL,15,FSlovakia, Spain, Sweden, Switzerland,
OL,16,Fand Turkey.
OL,18,FThe US, Canada, Mexico, Australia,
OL,19,FJapan, New Zealand, and South Korea
OL,20,Fare also members.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FThere are 13 associated countries,
OL,8,Fincluding Argentina, China, Egypt,
OL,9,FIndia, Indonesia, Kenya, Morocco,
OL,10,FSenegal, Singapore, South Africa,
OL,11,FThailand, Ukraine, and Vietnam.
OL,13,FFive countries - Brazil, Chile,
OL,14,FColombia, Israel, and Costa Rica - are
OL,15,Fcurrently in the accession process to
OL,16,Fbecome members.
OL,18,FHow much oil is there in reserves?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
