PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FMember countries hold more than 1.2
OL,8,Fbillion barrels of emergency oil
OL,9,Fstocks between them, the IEA said.
OL,11,FThere is also a further 600 million
OL,12,Fbarrels of industry stocks held by oil
OL,13,Fcompanies under government obligation,
OL,14,Fit said.
OL,16,FA barrel is equivalent to 42 US
OL,17,Fgallons (159 litres), which holds 20
OL,18,Fgallons (around 75 litres) of petrol,
OL,19,Faccording to the US Energy Information
OL,20,FAdministration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
