PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FHave emergency stocks been released
OL,8,Fbefore?
OL,10,FThis is the sixth release in the
OL,11,Fhistory of the IEA.
OL,13,FA total of 182 barrels of oil were
OL,14,Freleased across 2022 following
OL,15,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine, and 60
OL,16,Fmillion barrels were freed up in 2011
OL,17,Fdue to the civil war in Libya.
OL,19,FEmergency releases also happened after
OL,20,FHurricane Katrina in 2005 and during
OL,21,Fthe Gulf War in 1991.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FThe IEA executive director, Fatih
OL,8,FBirol, said on Wednesday: "The oil
OL,9,Fmarket challenges we are facing are
OL,10,Funprecedented in scale, therefore I am
OL,11,Fvery glad that IEA member countries
OL,12,Fhave responded with an emergency
OL,13,Fcollective action of unprecedented
OL,14,Fsize."
OL,16,FWhere are emergency stocks kept?
OL,18,FOil stocks are often kept offshore
OL,19,Ffrom the countries they belong to, at
OL,20,Findustry facilities known as terminals
OL,21,For processing plants.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FAs of May 2025, Czechia, Hungary,
OL,8,FAustria, Poland, Slovakia, and Greece
OL,9,Fwere the only EU countries to keep all
OL,10,Ftheir emergency stocks within their
OL,11,Fterritory. Out of the IEA European
OL,12,Fmembers. Luxembourg and Belgium were
OL,13,Fthe countries that kept most of their
OL,14,Foil abroad.
OL,16,FThe US keeps its oil reserves -
OL,17,Festimated to be more than 400 million
OL,18,Fbarrels earlier this year - in
OL,19,Funderground caverns in Texas and
OL,20,FLouisiana.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FThe UK's oil is mostly held by private
OL,8,Foil companies and fuel suppliers under
OL,9,Fgovernment regulations, with around
OL,10,F15% in overseas territories, such as
OL,11,FGermany, Belgium, and the Netherlands.
OL,13,FWho is participating in the release?
OL,15,FThe IEA said all of its 32 member
OL,16,Fcountries "unanimously agreed" to make
OL,17,Fthe 400 million barrels available on
OL,18,FWednesday, following a meeting between
OL,19,Fgovernments the day before.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FThe countries can individually decide
OL,8,Fwhether or not they participate.
OL,10,FThe UK has promised to release 13.5
OL,11,Fmillion barrels, although no time
OL,12,Fframe for this has been supplied.
OL,14,F"The way to protect families and
OL,15,Fbusinesses in the long run is to get
OL,16,Foff our dependency on global fossil
OL,17,Ffuel markets, and onto clean homegrown
OL,18,Fpower which we control," Energy
OL,19,FSecretary Ed Miliband said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FThe UK currently holds 76.6 million
OL,8,Fbarrels of oil stocks in total and has
OL,9,Fparticipated in all of the IEA's past
OL,10,Freleases, the Department for Energy
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FThe US is set to release 172 million
OL,14,Fbarrels over the next 120 days, US
OL,15,FSecretary of Energy Chris Wright said.
OL,17,FWhat impact will the oil release have?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,FReleasing emergency stocks will help
OL,8,Fcontain the surge in energy prices,
OL,9,Fbut it is not clear how quickly the
OL,10,Fbarrels will reach the market.
OL,12,FThe ultimate impact on markets and the
OL,13,Fbroader economy will depend on the
OL,14,Fduration of disruptions to transport
OL,15,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,16,Faccording to the IEA's March 2026 Oil
OL,17,FMarket Report, published on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773349949
OL,3,CHow does the world's emergency oil
OL,4,Csystem work ` and why is it being used
OL,5,Cnow?
OL,7,F"The coordinated emergency stock
OL,8,Frelease provides a significant and
OL,9,Fwelcome buffer, but in the absence of
OL,10,Fa swift resolution to the conflict, it
OL,11,Fremains a stopgap measure," it said.
OL,13,FDiesel and jet fuel markets are
OL,14,Fparticularly vulnerable to an extended
OL,15,Floss of production and exports, due to
OL,16,Flimited ability to increase output
OL,17,Felsewhere, but the suspension of
OL,18,Fflights at major Middle East airports
OL,19,Fhas reduced demand, the report said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
